                  <div class="highlight-box h5">
                    <p>ADB is a leading multilateral development bank supporting sustainable, inclusive, and resilient growth across Asia and the Pacific. Working with its members and partners, ADB provides quality development solutions to solve the region’s complex challenges.</p>
                    <p>Founded in 1966, ADB is owned by 69 members—50 from the region.</p>
