<div class="col-md-6">
<p class="h4 mb-1 heading">About ADB</p>
<div class="fs-note-2">
<p>ADB is a leading multilateral development bank supporting sustainable, inclusive, and resilient growth across Asia and the Pacific. Working with its members and partners to solve complex challenges together, ADB harnesses innovative financial tools and strategic partnerships to transform lives, build quality infrastructure, and safeguard our planet.</p>
<p>Founded in 1966, ADB is owned by 69 members—50 from the region.</p>
<h5 class="mb-1">Headquarters</h5>
<p class="mb-0">6 ADB Avenue, Mandaluyong City 1550, Metro Manila, Philippines</p>
<ul class="nav nav-compact flex-column flex-sm-row gap-md-3">
<li><a class="text-white" href="tel:+63286324444"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> +63 2 8632 4444</a></li>
<li><i class="fa-solid fa-fax"></i> +63 2 8636 2444</li>
</ul>
